headline: Suncor's Alberta Firebag Oil Sands Site Breaks Crude Output Record
summary: SU hit record crude output in October at its "Rock Star" Firebag site, strengthening the company's role amid production challenges.

headline: TC Energy & Hanwha Join Forces to Create Carbon-Free Power
summary: TRP & Hanwha Power Systems partners on an innovative sCO2 project to capture waste heat from natural gas and convert it into renewable energy.
